{"tid":1099583,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好執輸？多車搶先「霸位」　救護車呆困黃格","createTime":"2019-04-10T01:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T06:21:39.000Z","uid":225464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cf9dba02a056d4d86a078cb484807dc9d9d85f","tid":1099583,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:00:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔好執輸？多車搶先「霸位」 救護車呆困黃格</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2I9tkTi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I9tkTi&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=27565215\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2I9tkTi</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190410/photo/bkn-20190410081535038-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190410081842\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190410081535038-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190410081842&h=fadf26f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救護車在黃格內苦等近半分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n救護車一向分秒必爭。惟近日有救護車在沙田響號行駛時，不少車輛均「掂行掂過」，未有讓路，被網民炮轟︰「自私」。<br />\n<br />\n網友何定邦上載片段至Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」，畫面顯示，周一（8日）上午9時許，有救護車在大涌橋路響着警號衝燈，欲右轉入沙角街。<br />\n<br />\n惟當時不少車輛選擇繼續直行，即使前方車龍未退，有私家車及小巴仍搶在救護車前，駛入黃格。最終救護車被困在黃格內，苦候約半分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民怒斥：「自X私」、「明塞黃格都要頂，黐線」。有人慨嘆：「香港啲司機真係冇呢方面嘅意識」、「如果傷者係佢哋家人，會希望遇到同樣待遇嗎」？<br />\n<br />\n根據《道路交通（交通管制）規例》第46條，道路上車輛的司機必須讓路或採取一切可能的行動，讓路給任何正在發出警報聲響或發出閃光警標的警車、消防服務或消防裝置車輛、救護車或海關服務車輛。任何人無合理辯解而違反上述規定即屬違法，可被判罰款港幣2,000元。"},{"pid":"ab2981bd9797c0e6e4cd6b5c641b0f077168234d","tid":1099583,"uid":220431,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:03:11.000Z","msg":"中國人係咁"},{"pid":"44d790348d149ecc3eea5d423ed061fc544bd321","tid":1099583,"uid":120715,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"斑馬線都係啦<br />\n一到綠燈公仔<br />\n個個行人掛住行<br />\n冇諗過讓俾響晒燈嘅救護車"},{"pid":"0c10523041da571b0af9b7dd40006773e613efc2","tid":1099583,"uid":5499,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"d車成日踩入黃格停低嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別dc9"},{"pid":"56ada60a9420102fd8536b6d69697bcf319f2ded","tid":1099583,"uid":26050,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"拎過條cam片報1823,逐個車牌罰$2000有冇得諗"},{"pid":"03e514801e29732e15df755a5be418a60ea5a078","tid":1099583,"uid":60860,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:25:05.000Z","msg":"個個都心諗我唔讓後面會讓<br />\n結果咪前車唔讓我老閪都唔讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小農dna執輸行頭慘過拜家"},{"pid":"be5f8f9b4c2f65bc903eb0ea182d868a93016724","tid":1099583,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"唔知點解香港司機真係咁垃圾"},{"pid":"8ab217a7d0b47208022065d6be7aa14cbf8d0f4d","tid":1099583,"uid":89801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ada60a9420102fd8536b6d69697bcf319f2ded","tid":1099583,"uid":26050,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"拎過條cam片報1823,逐個車牌罰$2000有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"可以咁做<br />\n如果你有條片 我支持你咁做<br />\n但你要上警署落口供警察先會做野"},{"pid":"9761a1ec512f4c0de007289b22fb0312e976250a","tid":1099583,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ada60a9420102fd8536b6d69697bcf319f2ded","tid":1099583,"uid":26050,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"拎過條cam片報1823,逐個車牌罰$2000有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"條片係係拍嘅支持你咁做"},{"pid":"e584cc994e95bbd7bcaface0978e37ddb5c6cf78","tid":1099583,"uid":201828,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"人在外地，鬼佬真係會守呢樣規矩。好多時離遠聽到，唔理係邊個方向，大家都一齊收油駛埋一邊，預俾佢過，情形就好似摩西分紅海咁。<br />\n<br />\n而緊急車輛過左，大家又會乖乖咁跟番之前次序行車，好少見有人成機跟車尾打尖。而香港，不下一次見啲仆街貼住白車嘅車尾，成機打尖。"},{"pid":"ccba6512147deebe09e39b594a4c78cf1d83c22e","tid":1099583,"uid":24980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"岩嫁啦，香港人五十步笑百步就叻，實際都係支那式風格"},{"pid":"60f8879e812f14e7233ba52c9d48f97205819653","tid":1099583,"uid":24980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"be5f8f9b4c2f65bc903eb0ea182d868a93016724","tid":1099583,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"唔知點解香港司機真係咁垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"特別係堆搵食車，重有R佛狗"},{"pid":"b39eb0822b92b27f38f4b89a0ecaff2c3f1769f1","tid":1099583,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdcda91ca2060ca028dcd321fc8f14d54b873b97","tid":1099583,"uid":9193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"其實救護車上面有cam<br />\n咁樣停黃格嘅好大機會已經舉報晒"},{"pid":"2d2488e69d9c55924a54dc100e12bb6722c95871","tid":1099583,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"其實係罰得太輕既問題"},{"pid":"8f9d749ac4edd2b94217d72071570bd686a7c8df","tid":1099583,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"不如話救護司機無技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你夠膽踩油, 我唔信唔讓比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講, 你要人專登慢車, 其實好撚危險<br />\n後面跟貼d 就一野炒埋來<br />\n唔識渣車咪9 up"},{"pid":"d39c901cd063b19a78223c40f39c73e4c309bc42","tid":1099583,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"白色轉左黃色<br />\n可能唔知呢部咩車"},{"pid":"2d9ed188320c7227463dbc3d18c83054d55f896b","tid":1099583,"uid":152003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實救護車上面有cam<br />\n咁樣停黃格嘅好大機會已經舉報晒</blockquote><br />\n你諗多左 救護員上寫字樓同官講 我想開Cam拎條片舉報市民唔喺我去車個陣唔讓路 你覺得個官會比咩反應你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd740867b68ccdfcfda60f9f79ecd3b97b2ffad9","tid":1099583,"uid":7934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d39c901cd063b19a78223c40f39c73e4c309bc42","tid":1099583,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"白色轉左黃色<br />\n可能唔知呢部咩車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"唔識字學咩人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a140e2cfb93592cd50565e556c5815d407514b","tid":1099583,"uid":153391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以好似警車咁裝個speaker<br />\n一俾人頂住就爆咪：「前面班7頭死撚開呀，而家死人冧樓呀！」"},{"pid":"5ea02783d79999429b301e9db67efd8d8925c3bd","tid":1099583,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a140e2cfb93592cd50565e556c5815d407514b","tid":1099583,"uid":153391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以好似警車咁裝個speaker<br />\n一俾人頂住就爆咪：「前面班7頭死撚開呀，而家死人冧樓呀！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"好似係有，但好少用"},{"pid":"44a344e135fb6a5bcdbf5424353f6ce922c7c995","tid":1099583,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊個國家 每架救護車都配有3架鐵馬輪流係前面3個路口截車 好有效率 不過香港地細人又多 應該無咩機會"},{"pid":"6549399505c23c17596437814c563ba4dd8e55cf","tid":1099583,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea02783d79999429b301e9db67efd8d8925c3bd","tid":1099583,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a140e2cfb93592cd50565e556c5815d407514b","tid":1099583,"uid":153391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以好似警車咁裝個speaker<br />\n一俾人頂住就爆咪：「前面班7頭死撚開呀，而家死人冧樓呀！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"好似係有，但好少用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解救護車司機個個都好保守<br />\n唔係叫你亂黎, 橫衡直撞<br />\n而係cut下線爬頭都唔太會, 明知香港D司機唔太鐘意移開架車讓<br />\n成條直路隔離線/或者對面線無車, 救護車都好少會cut左cut右<br />\n我覺得唔使咁保守<br />\n同埋普遍救護車個警號開得好細聲, 完全唔夠力去迫人讓路<br />\n警車唔使講開得好快, 消防車通常都幾狠,有D ON9頂住都會BU鳩你<br />\n唯獨係救護車比人擋死左, 仲會停左個警號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2906d44777e4e4f0328a2bff8df6717097d585","tid":1099583,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6549399505c23c17596437814c563ba4dd8e55cf","tid":1099583,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea02783d79999429b301e9db67efd8d8925c3bd","tid":1099583,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a140e2cfb93592cd50565e556c5815d407514b","tid":1099583,"uid":153391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以好似警車咁裝個speaker<br />\n一俾人頂住就爆咪：「前面班7頭死撚開呀，而家死人冧樓呀！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"好似係有，但好少用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解救護車司機個個都好保守<br />\n唔係叫你亂黎, 橫衡直撞<br />\n而係cut下線爬頭都唔太會, 明知香港D司機唔太鐘意移開架車讓<br />\n成條直路隔離線/或者對面線無車, 救護車都好少會cut左cut右<br />\n我覺得唔使咁保守<br />\n同埋普遍救護車個警號開得好細聲, 完全唔夠力去迫人讓路<br />\n警車唔使講開得好快, 消防車通常都幾狠,有D ON9頂住都會BU鳩你<br />\n唯獨係救護車比人擋死左, 仲會停左個警號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"因為救護既官唔會保你<br />\n只係踩多你兩腳"},{"pid":"b24d3c2bb8a0f4881a22433ee4b18686fba0d0b1","tid":1099583,"uid":224561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd2906d44777e4e4f0328a2bff8df6717097d585","tid":1099583,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6549399505c23c17596437814c563ba4dd8e55cf","tid":1099583,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea02783d79999429b301e9db67efd8d8925c3bd","tid":1099583,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"好似係有，但好少用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解救護車司機個個都好保守<br />\n唔係叫你亂黎, 橫衡直撞<br />\n而係cut下線爬頭都唔太會, 明知香港D司機唔太鐘意移開架車讓<br />\n成條直路隔離線/或者對面線無車, 救護車